metadata.name: Tyranite Drill
metadata.description: The Tyranite Drill is a machine built by Tyranz engineers in order to extract the primary source of energy in the New World: the Tyranite. Engineers have built only 165 of them and believe are sufficient to extract an amount needed for the development of society. This exclusive machinery has unrivaled utilities and it gives you premium access to the Tyranz Kingdom. Learn more on our Discord and Website
